data.description: Meticulously maintained home featuring 5 BRs, 3 full baths, end-of-road privacy, a stream w/waterfall & a zen garden! Main-level living featuring an open floor plan boasting a large living area w/gas-log fireplace. XL kitchen with ample cabinet & counter space, stainless appliances & breakfast bar that adjoins the dining area. Large primary bedroom with tray ceiling, walk-in closet & ensuite bath w/ dual vanities, ceramic tile step-in shower & a pet-washing sink. Opposite the living area are the 2nd and 3rd bedrooms, 2nd bath & mudroom. Upstairs features the 2nd huge living area that can be accessed from the exterior & interior, 4th & 5th bedrooms, 3rd full bath, plus a space for a kitchenette & tons of storage; there is enough room for two families in this home! The exterior features a front porch, rear attached carport with a handicap ramp, storage building & paved driveway with ample parking. The nature lover will enjoy the garden area, Tranquil & peaceful living!
